layout.house_prompt: A hair salon with a salon floor, a waiting area, a storage room, and a bathroom. The salon floor has two salon chairs positioned in front of two mirrors on the wall, facing them. The waiting area has a sofa and a coffee table. The storage room has shelves with bottles. The bathroom has a toilet and a sink.

salon_floor.text_description: A modern commercial hair salon main floor with two salon chairs positioned in front of two wall-mounted mirrors, facing the mirrors; clean, bright, professional styling area.

waiting_area.text_description: A modern commercial salon waiting area with a sofa and a coffee table; welcoming reception-side space with clear circulation.

vestibule.text_description: A small modern commercial entry vestibule/buffer space for the salon; simple clean finishes and clear wayfinding.

bathroom.text_description: A compact modern commercial bathroom with a toilet and a sink; privacy-focused access from the reception/entry side.

storage_room.text_description: A modern commercial storage room with sturdy shelves holding bottles of hair products; easy-clean floors suitable for shelving loads.
